    "description": "Nomura System Corporation Co, Ltd. provides ERP solutions in Japan. The company offers SAP ERP consulting services, including business process reform plan development, IT investment plan development, and IT diagnostics; project preparation, business design, and additional development design; implementation and preparation for go-live; and going-out support, and operation and maintenance services. It also provides short-term implementation plan; SAP on HANA migration service; and SAP new UX service. In addition, the company offers robotic process automation, web development, and big data consulting services. Further, it provides Rcas-Win, a SAP ERP accounting solution; Zex-One, a SAP EMS fixed asset solution; GeeBBIT, a SAP ERP appendix 16 solutions; Jet-One, a SAP ERP human resources solutions; SAP SucessFactors, a talent management solutions; BeeBBit, a SAP ERP human resources/BI solution; XronoLink, a web based attendance management solution; Bl-Vivid, a SAP business analytics solution; and project resilience theory. Nomura System Corporation Co, Ltd. was incorporated in 1986 and is headquartered in Shibuya, Japan."
